402
00:44:38,320 --> 00:44:40,719
[SPEAKER_01] On je zapravo zbog te povrede kralježnice...

403
00:44:40,719 --> 00:44:43,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ima prometnu nesreću gdje ga auto...

404
00:44:43,679 --> 00:44:45,760
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da, za vreme biciklizma da...

405
00:44:45,760 --> 00:44:46,860
[SPEAKER_01] I onda je ono u stvari,

406
00:44:47,360 --> 00:44:49,780
[SPEAKER_01] bilo je ono odluka očeli ga operirati,

407
00:44:49,780 --> 00:44:51,460
[SPEAKER_01] pa da bude u kolicima cijeli živo,

408
00:44:51,460 --> 00:44:54,099
[SPEAKER_01] a ima je 19 godina, 20, kad se to desilo,

409
00:44:54,099 --> 00:44:57,119
