[SPEAKER_01] i podijelio ih je u tri zdjelice,

425
00:45:31,719 --> 00:45:33,199
[SPEAKER_01] u jednoj je bila otopina,

426
00:45:33,199 --> 00:45:35,219
[SPEAKER_01] kao gdje se stvaraju krvatorni organi,

427
00:45:35,219 --> 00:45:36,260
[SPEAKER_01] u drugoj kost,

428
00:45:36,260 --> 00:45:37,519
[SPEAKER_01] u trećoj mišići, mislim.

429
00:45:37,880 --> 00:45:40,099
[SPEAKER_01] i nakon oni se jako brzo su te stanice,

430
00:45:40,099 --> 00:45:40,940
[SPEAKER_01] de facto,

431
00:45:40,940 --> 00:45:43,300
[SPEAKER_01] poveća se njihov broj

432
00:45:43,300 --> 00:45:45,300
[SPEAKER_01] i onda je,

433
00:45:45,300 --> 00:45:47,440
[SPEAKER_01] tamo gdje je bila otopina za krvi,

434
00:45:47,440 --> 00:45:49,260
[SPEAKER_01] su se stvorili krvne stanice,

435
00:45:49,260 --> 00:45:50,599
[SPEAKER_01] tu mišići, tu koste.

436
00:45:50,659 --> 00:45:55,260
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, otopina unutra u koju on stavio,

437
00:45:55,260 --> 00:45:56,360
