[SPEAKER_01] koje nam stalno idu,

454
00:46:29,519 --> 00:46:30,820
[SPEAKER_01] mislim, po glavi.

455
00:46:30,820 --> 00:46:33,539
[SPEAKER_01] I mislite, niste ni svjesni šta se sve pet,

456
