[SPEAKER_01] imao isto dvije grupe.

478
00:47:16,659 --> 00:47:19,519
[SPEAKER_01] Jednoj grupi je dao zadatak

479
00:47:19,519 --> 00:47:22,119
[SPEAKER_01] da svako jutro i svaku večer

480
00:47:22,119 --> 00:47:25,059
[SPEAKER_01] 20 puta ponovi onu slavnu rečenicu,

481
00:47:25,059 --> 00:47:27,320
[SPEAKER_01] svaki dan u svakom pogledu

482
00:47:27,320 --> 00:47:28,539
[SPEAKER_01] sve više napredujem,

483
00:47:28,539 --> 00:47:30,059
[SPEAKER_01] ili sve mi je bolje, bolje sam.

484
00:47:30,059 --> 00:47:32,800
[SPEAKER_01] Znači 20 puta jutro,

485
00:47:32,800 --> 00:47:35,239
[SPEAKER_01] osvješeno na glas,

486
00:47:35,239 --> 00:47:36,619
[SPEAKER_01] da znaš i gledaš se u špiglu

487
00:47:36,619 --> 00:47:37,280
[SPEAKER_01] i to govoriš.

488
00:47:37,280 --> 00:47:40,039
[SPEAKER_01] A druga grupa koja su imala iste simptome,

489
00:47:40,039 --> 00:47:41,440
[SPEAKER_01] oni su dobivali ljekove

490
00:47:41,440 --> 00:47:42,659
[SPEAKER_01] i nisu ništa pone.

491
00:47:42,659 --> 00:47:45,599
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su za mjesec dana izašli iz bolnice

492
00:47:45,599 --> 00:47:48,460
[SPEAKER_01] i veselo oporavljeni,

493
00:47:48,460 --> 00:47:50,460
[SPEAKER_01] a nažalost ona grupa koja je bila

494
00:47:50,460 --> 00:47:52,059
[SPEAKER_01] samo na terapiji ljekovima

495
00:47:52,059 --> 00:47:53,960
[SPEAKER_01] nije bila tako dobro oporavljena.

496
00:47:54,400 --> 00:47:56,519
[SPEAKER_01] I to je, isto tada nije ono bilo

497
00:47:56,519 --> 00:47:57,260
[SPEAKER_01] upotrebljavano,

498
00:47:57,260 --> 00:47:59,940
[SPEAKER_01] 1925. 6. kada to knjigo ono

499
00:47:59,940 --> 00:48:01,920
[SPEAKER_01] na te neko pogledao i ostavio,

500
00:48:01,920 --> 00:48:03,239
[SPEAKER_01] ali tek i poslije se vidjelo

501
00:48:03,239 --> 00:48:05,960
[SPEAKER_01] koliko je te fakto to snažno

502
00:48:05,960 --> 00:48:08,139
[SPEAKER_01] i korisno, jer se mogu i ti svi razni

503
00:48:08,139 --> 00:48:09,699
[SPEAKER_01] neurotransmiteri izmjeriti

504
00:48:09,699 --> 00:48:11,380
[SPEAKER_01] prije početka i poslije.

505
00:48:11,380 --> 00:48:13,159
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, te naše misli su vam

506
00:48:13,159 --> 00:48:14,679
[SPEAKER_01] nevjerovacno važne.

507
00:48:14,679 --> 00:48:17,079
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam jedno predavanje baš imala

508
00:48:17,079 --> 00:48:18,900
[SPEAKER_01] na velikom kongresu u Dubrovniku

509
00:48:18,900 --> 00:48:21,019
[SPEAKER_01] kontroverze u neurologiji ovo proljeće

510
00:48:21,019 --> 00:48:23,800
[SPEAKER_01] i ono bilo preko tisuću sudionika

511
00:48:23,800 --> 00:48:25,239
[SPEAKER_01] praktički iz pola svijeta

512
00:48:25,239 --> 00:48:27,820
[SPEAKER_01] i onda, dakle, sad da sam bila

513
00:48:27,820 --> 00:48:30,400
[SPEAKER_01] suorganizator toga jer je bila u Dubrovniku,

514
00:48:30,400 --> 00:48:33,119
[SPEAKER_01] onda su mi, zamolim da ja prvo

515
00:48:33,119 --> 00:48:34,480
[SPEAKER_01] plenarno predavanje održem,

516
00:48:34,480 --> 00:48:36,099
[SPEAKER_01] neke ja izaberem temu

517
00:48:36,099 --> 00:48:37,320
[SPEAKER_01] i onda sam izabrala temu

518
00:48:37,320 --> 00:48:39,719
[SPEAKER_01] neuroplastičnost u zravlju i bolesti,

519
00:48:39,719 --> 00:48:42,039
[SPEAKER_01] kao neuroplasticity in health and disease.

520
00:48:42,440 --> 00:48:44,679
[SPEAKER_01] i onda sam se jako bavila tim da još vidim

521
00:48:44,679 --> 00:48:46,659
[SPEAKER_01] šta drugi ljudi od toj neuroplastičnosti

522
00:48:46,659 --> 00:48:48,280
[SPEAKER_01] pišu, radu, eksperimenta i tako.

523
00:48:48,280 --> 00:48:50,780
[SPEAKER_01] I onda naišla sam baš na tih nekoliko

524
00:48:50,780 --> 00:48:53,519
[SPEAKER_01] jako važnih istraživanja i dokaza.

525
00:48:53,519 --> 00:48:55,760
