526
00:48:55,760 --> 00:48:58,559
[SPEAKER_01] ljubav ta, evo, to je jedan eksperiment.

527
00:48:58,559 --> 00:49:00,599
[SPEAKER_01] Daimonza mogu možda ga isto spomenuti,

528
00:49:00,599 --> 00:49:02,699
[SPEAKER_01] to je osam da je s druge objavljeno u časopisu.

529
00:49:03,199 --> 00:49:06,659
[SPEAKER_01] Dajmons je imao, istraživao sa štakorima

530
00:49:06,659 --> 00:49:10,300
[SPEAKER_01] neki lijek ili, ne znam, dugovječnost u glavu.

531
00:49:10,300 --> 00:49:12,780
[SPEAKER_01] Dva je imao kaveza, u jednom je bio

532
00:49:12,780 --> 00:49:17,059
[SPEAKER_01] isti, mislim, isti karakteristika štakori.

533
00:49:17,059 --> 00:49:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ovi su dobivali hranu i vodu,

534
00:49:20,000 --> 00:49:22,619
[SPEAKER_01] a u drugom kavezu isto to,

535
00:49:22,619 --> 00:49:25,079
[SPEAKER_01] ali oni ih je gladio, s njima razgovarao,

536
00:49:25,079 --> 00:49:28,119
[SPEAKER_01] puštao im glazbu i bili su u ovak jednom kontaktu,

537
00:49:28,119 --> 00:49:30,480
[SPEAKER_01] volio ih je i pokazivao im da ih voli.

538
00:49:31,000 --> 00:49:33,519
[SPEAKER_01] I oni su on 50% vremena dulje živjeli

539
00:49:33,519 --> 00:49:35,639
[SPEAKER_01] i, mislim, to nije izmišljotina,

540
00:49:35,639 --> 00:49:38,500
[SPEAKER_01] nego je to stvarno scientific proof dokaz

541
00:49:38,500 --> 00:49:40,739
[SPEAKER_01] i to je jedan od prvih, pokazate,

542
00:49:40,739 --> 00:49:44,079
