01:06:14,219 --> 01:06:15,780
[SPEAKER_01] je to straga u mozgu,

1171
01:06:15,780 --> 01:06:18,739
[SPEAKER_01] negdje između baze mozga i terebruma,

1172
01:06:18,739 --> 01:06:21,820
[SPEAKER_01] onda je Descartes je rekao da je to zapravo

1173
01:06:21,820 --> 01:06:23,239
[SPEAKER_01] pinealna žljezda,

1174
01:06:23,239 --> 01:06:24,320
[SPEAKER_01] to je ono u sredini,

1175
01:06:24,320 --> 01:06:26,179
[SPEAKER_01] kao, nisi to kao kažemo,

1176
01:06:26,280 --> 01:06:29,619
[SPEAKER_01] treća okona, znači, iza nosa u dubini ravno linija,

1177
01:06:29,619 --> 01:06:31,099
[SPEAKER_01] to je u stvari jedina žljezda

1178
01:06:31,099 --> 01:06:32,400
[SPEAKER_01] koja je neparna u mozu,

1179
01:06:32,400 --> 01:06:35,219
[SPEAKER_01] znači, to je kao po njemu bila sjelo duše,

1180
01:06:35,219 --> 01:06:35,739
[SPEAKER_01] jer imate,

1181
01:06:35,739 --> 01:06:38,099
[SPEAKER_01] druge su ljeva i desna,

1182
01:06:38,099 --> 01:06:39,400
[SPEAKER_01] ovo je kao u sredini,

1183
01:06:39,400 --> 01:06:39,980
[SPEAKER_01] pa je to,

1184
01:06:39,980 --> 01:06:41,760
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, tamo,

1185
01:06:41,760 --> 01:06:45,219
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, puno je bilo tih opisivanja različitih

1186
01:06:45,219 --> 01:06:49,059
[SPEAKER_01] i to su neke filozofske priče i škole i tako,

1187
01:06:49,119 --> 01:06:51,880
[SPEAKER_01] ja mislim da, mislim, duša ne može nestat,

1188
01:06:51,880 --> 01:06:54,260
[SPEAKER_01] materija ne može nestat,

1189
01:06:54,260 --> 01:06:56,059
[SPEAKER_01] znači, mi smo svi zapravo,

1190
01:06:56,059 --> 01:06:58,780
[SPEAKER_01] ta energija je onda i materija

1191
01:06:58,780 --> 01:07:00,179
[SPEAKER_01] i to je to.

1192
01:07:00,179 --> 01:07:03,079
[SPEAKER_01] Prema tome, duša je najvažnija u stvari.

1193
01:07:03,079 --> 01:07:03,900
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1194
01:07:06,400 --> 01:07:07,440
[SPEAKER_00] Kako, recimo,

1195
01:07:07,440 --> 01:07:12,579
[SPEAKER_00] kao neuropsihijatar,

1196
01:07:12,579 --> 01:07:16,139
[SPEAKER_00] objašnjavate, recimo, našu svijest

1197
01:07:16,139 --> 01:07:18,739
[SPEAKER_00] ili realnost koju percipiramo uopće?

1198
01:07:18,739 --> 01:07:20,059
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, svijest, zapravo,

1199
01:07:20,059 --> 01:07:21,059
[SPEAKER_01] realnost,

1200
01:07:21,059 --> 01:07:25,659
[SPEAKER_01] mislim, to je zapravo prepoznavanje onog oko nas,

1201
01:07:25,659 --> 01:07:27,420
[SPEAKER_01] jer to je ta percepcija, de facto.

1202
01:07:27,420 --> 01:07:29,239
[SPEAKER_01] Mi imamo impulse koje dobivamo

1203
01:07:29,239 --> 01:07:31,079
[SPEAKER_01] iz okoline i, znači,

1204
01:07:31,079 --> 01:07:34,400
[SPEAKER_01] i to možemo onda na neki način

1205
01:07:34,400 --> 01:07:38,340
[SPEAKER_01] objasniti svojim dosadašnjim iskustvima,

1206
01:07:38,340 --> 01:07:41,840
[SPEAKER_01] znanjem, prethodnim nekim događanjima,

1207
01:07:41,840 --> 01:07:44,159
[SPEAKER_01] ali, zapravo, tu svijest,

1208
01:07:44,159 --> 01:07:48,099
[SPEAKER_01] de facto, isto nismo baš ono previše objasnili,

1209
01:07:48,099 --> 01:07:49,940
[SPEAKER_01] ima puno istraživanja koje govore,

1210
01:07:49,940 --> 01:07:52,380
[SPEAKER_01] čak nalaze i neke grupe neurona

1211
01:07:52,380 --> 01:07:54,360
[SPEAKER_01] koje su možda zaduženi za ono,

1212
01:07:54,360 --> 01:07:55,619
[SPEAKER_01] da pokažu

1213
01:07:55,619 --> 01:07:59,579
[SPEAKER_01] koji dio mozga bi bio taj ko je tu svijestan,

1214
01:07:59,579 --> 01:08:00,260
[SPEAKER_01] ali, zapravo, je,

1215
01:08:00,260 --> 01:08:03,159
[SPEAKER_01] to je mozak, de facto,

1216
01:08:03,159 --> 01:08:04,980
[SPEAKER_01] on nam omogućuje da

1217
01:08:04,980 --> 01:08:08,159
[SPEAKER_01] svjesno nosimo se kroz život,

1218
01:08:08,159 --> 01:08:10,420
[SPEAKER_01] a kako ćemo to,

1219
01:08:10,420 --> 01:08:12,659
[SPEAKER_01] percepcija i svijest zapravo nije ista,

1220
01:08:12,659 --> 01:08:14,380
[SPEAKER_01] jer, veli, ta percepcija ovisi o

1221
01:08:14,380 --> 01:08:17,180
[SPEAKER_01] našim dosadašnjim, ja mislim,

1222
01:08:17,180 --> 01:08:19,439
[SPEAKER_01] znanjima i načinima razmišljenja,

1223
01:08:19,439 --> 01:08:21,979
[SPEAKER_01] jer možda ono što smo prije pričali,

1224
01:08:21,979 --> 01:08:23,100
[SPEAKER_01] reakcija na, recimo,

1225
01:08:23,100 --> 01:08:25,020
[SPEAKER_01] neki događaj, tako je i percepcija,

1226
01:08:25,020 --> 01:08:27,060
[SPEAKER_01] možda je isto drugačija kod nekih ljudi.

1227
01:08:27,439 --> 01:08:29,300
[SPEAKER_01] Nekom se jedna slika jako sviđa,

1228
01:08:29,300 --> 01:08:32,140
[SPEAKER_01] a vama se možda ne sviđa neka,

1229
01:08:32,140 --> 01:08:34,819
[SPEAKER_01] ili neka glazba koju ja obožavam,

1230
01:08:34,819 --> 01:08:36,640
[SPEAKER_01] ali, veli, nema mi to slušati.

1231
01:08:36,640 --> 01:08:39,319
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, evo, to je ta raznolikost,

1232
01:08:39,319 --> 01:08:41,039
[SPEAKER_01] zato smo mi to posebni,

1233
01:08:41,039 --> 01:08:42,819
[SPEAKER_01] svako od nas je zapravo za sebe

1234
01:08:42,819 --> 01:08:44,859
[SPEAKER_01] jedan entitet drugačiji,

1235
01:08:44,979 --> 01:08:46,819
[SPEAKER_01] i zato je o tom što pričamo,

1236
01:08:46,819 --> 01:08:48,319
[SPEAKER_01] da ta empatija važna,

1237
01:08:48,319 --> 01:08:49,720
[SPEAKER_01] da se nastojimo razumijeti

1238
01:08:49,720 --> 01:08:52,140
[SPEAKER_01] i omogućiti da svaki u tom svom

1239
01:08:52,140 --> 01:08:54,180
[SPEAKER_01] najbolje brodi.

1240
01:08:54,180 --> 01:08:57,859
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, percepcije su stvarno različite,

1241
01:08:57,859 --> 01:08:59,619
[SPEAKER_01] ovisno o nizu stvari.

1242
01:08:59,619 --> 01:09:04,619
[SPEAKER_00] Što možete reći uopće o povezanosti?

1243
01:09:04,619 --> 01:09:06,199
[SPEAKER_00] Malo smo spomnili na početku,

1244
01:09:06,199 --> 01:09:09,239
[SPEAKER_00] bilo veza između mozga i crijeva,

1245
01:09:09,239 --> 01:09:10,300
[SPEAKER_00] veza između srca i...

1246
01:09:10,300 --> 01:09:11,579
[SPEAKER_01] To je sad jako postalo...

1247
01:09:11,579 --> 01:09:11,960
[SPEAKER_00] Mozga.

1248
01:09:11,960 --> 01:09:14,420
[SPEAKER_01] To je postalo sad jako velika jedna,

1249
01:09:14,420 --> 01:09:16,500
[SPEAKER_01] zapravo, veliko istraživanje,

1250
01:09:16,500 --> 01:09:19,340
[SPEAKER_01] kao mozak vaš drug...

1251
01:09:19,340 --> 01:09:20,939
[SPEAKER_01] Ove, crijeva vaš drugi mozak.

1252
01:09:20,939 --> 01:09:22,560
[SPEAKER_01] To je ono, got your second brain.

1253
01:09:22,560 --> 01:09:23,920
[SPEAKER_01] To se sad tako zove.

1254
01:09:23,920 --> 01:09:26,260
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, cijeli taj, mogu reći,

1255
01:09:26,260 --> 01:09:28,300
[SPEAKER_01] istraživanje, odnosno pristup,

1256
01:09:28,300 --> 01:09:30,720
[SPEAKER_01] i to je sad možda nekih 20 godina,

1257
01:09:30,720 --> 01:09:32,319
[SPEAKER_01] malo manje možda prisutno.

1258
01:09:32,319 --> 01:09:34,319
[SPEAKER_01] I istraživanje su krenula,

1259
01:09:34,319 --> 01:09:36,960
[SPEAKER_01] napravo od palesnika s Parkinsonovom bolešću,

1260
01:09:36,960 --> 01:09:38,760
[SPEAKER_01] kad su vidjeli da oni imaju neke probleme

1261
01:09:38,760 --> 01:09:41,439
[SPEAKER_01] sa prehranom, sa crijevima i tako,

1262
01:09:41,439 --> 01:09:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] i onda su vam našli zapravo da je manjak

1263
01:09:44,000 --> 01:09:45,979
[SPEAKER_01] dopamina.

1264
01:09:45,979 --> 01:09:48,380
[SPEAKER_01] A dopamin je jedan neurotransmiter

1265
01:09:48,380 --> 01:09:53,039
[SPEAKER_01] i hormon koji omogućuje niz stvari u organizmu,

1266
01:09:53,039 --> 01:09:54,600
[SPEAKER_01] a kod Parkinsonove bolesti

1267
01:09:54,600 --> 01:09:56,859
[SPEAKER_01] ga nema dovoljno,

1268
01:09:56,859 --> 01:09:59,159
[SPEAKER_01] on se izlučuje u onoj crnoj jezgri

1269
01:09:59,159 --> 01:10:01,800
[SPEAKER_01] u mozgu,

1270
01:10:01,800 --> 01:10:05,119
[SPEAKER_01] ali se 50% dopamina izlučuje

1271
01:10:05,119 --> 01:10:06,779
[SPEAKER_01] iz sluznice tankog crijeva.

1272
01:10:07,260 --> 01:10:09,140
[SPEAKER_01] i to se onda vidjelo istraživanjima,

1273
01:10:09,140 --> 01:10:11,140
[SPEAKER_01] da je ta količina dopamina,

1274
01:10:11,140 --> 01:10:12,319
[SPEAKER_01] kojeg nije dovoljno,

1275
01:10:12,319 --> 01:10:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] nema dovoljno pa se simptomi Parkinsonove bolesti

1276
01:10:15,000 --> 01:10:16,239
[SPEAKER_01] zato su izraženi,

1277
01:10:16,239 --> 01:10:18,920
[SPEAKER_01] da je to ipak izgleda zbog tog što

1278
01:10:18,920 --> 01:10:21,479
[SPEAKER_01] ovog ima manje koji se izlučuje iz strijeva.

1279
01:10:21,479 --> 01:10:22,479
[SPEAKER_01] Onda su vam našli da

1280
01:10:22,479 --> 01:10:24,899
[SPEAKER_01] 90% serotonina,

1281
01:10:24,899 --> 01:10:26,500
[SPEAKER_01] ono ko smo spominjali smo ga,

1282
01:10:26,500 --> 01:10:28,899
[SPEAKER_01] znači kao hormon sreće na neki način,

1283
01:10:28,899 --> 01:10:30,359
[SPEAKER_01] se izlučuje iz strijeva.

1284
01:10:30,439 --> 01:10:34,100
[SPEAKER_01] znači niz bolesti se de facto dogodi,

1285
01:10:34,100 --> 01:10:38,600
[SPEAKER_01] jer je ta količina koja nam je potrebna za funkcioniranje

1286
01:10:38,600 --> 01:10:44,060
[SPEAKER_01] cijelog organizma preko tih uputa strane mozga

1287
01:10:44,060 --> 01:10:48,260
[SPEAKER_01] se ne događa jer su crijeva ne funkcioniraju kako treba.

1288
01:10:48,260 --> 01:10:51,920
[SPEAKER_01] Recimo depresija vam je jedan od isto bolesti

1289
01:10:51,920 --> 01:10:52,739
[SPEAKER_01] za koje se misli,

1290
01:10:52,739 --> 01:10:54,880
[SPEAKER_01] jer tog serotonina onda nema dovoljno,

1291
01:10:54,960 --> 01:10:56,800
[SPEAKER_01] ako je probava loša.

1292
01:10:56,800 --> 01:10:58,079
[SPEAKER_01] I zato se počelo s im.

1293
01:10:58,079 --> 01:11:01,119
[SPEAKER_01] Mi imamo te triljune ovih bakterija

1294
01:11:01,119 --> 01:11:02,039
[SPEAKER_01] koje su nam dobre,

1295
01:11:02,039 --> 01:11:02,939
[SPEAKER_01] koje nam trebaju,

1296
01:11:02,939 --> 01:11:05,619
[SPEAKER_01] koje omogućuju metabolizam i sve skupa,

1297
01:11:05,619 --> 01:11:07,520
[SPEAKER_01] to su ti microbiome,

1298
01:11:07,520 --> 01:11:08,760
[SPEAKER_01] znači mikrobiota,

1299
01:11:08,760 --> 01:11:10,880
[SPEAKER_01] to se mora funkcionirati lijepo

1300
01:11:10,880 --> 01:11:12,380
[SPEAKER_01] i da probava bude kak treba

1301
01:11:12,380 --> 01:11:14,260
[SPEAKER_01] i onda da de facto

1302
01:11:14,260 --> 01:11:16,520
[SPEAKER_01] se sve je dobro,

1303
01:11:16,520 --> 01:11:17,220
[SPEAKER_01] nema bolesti.

1304
01:11:17,220 --> 01:11:17,779
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim,

1305
01:11:17,779 --> 01:11:19,699
[SPEAKER_01] ako se ljudi loše hrane,

1306
01:11:19,699 --> 01:11:22,079
[SPEAKER_01] ako prevladavaju to neke loše bakterije,

1307
01:11:22,079 --> 01:11:24,380
[SPEAKER_01] ako zbog stresa

1308
01:11:24,380 --> 01:11:25,920
[SPEAKER_01] dolazi od one strahote,

1309
01:11:25,920 --> 01:11:26,800
[SPEAKER_01] izlučivanja,

1310
01:11:26,800 --> 01:11:29,340
[SPEAKER_01] znači manjka kortizola,

1311
01:11:29,340 --> 01:11:31,199
[SPEAKER_01] onda se znači imunitetu uništava,

1312
01:11:31,199 --> 01:11:32,819
[SPEAKER_01] a to je najčešća priča

1313
01:11:32,819 --> 01:11:35,300
[SPEAKER_01] zašto se to onda s tim crjevima dogodi,

1314
01:11:35,300 --> 01:11:37,819
[SPEAKER_01] onda se to manifestira bolestima,

1315
01:11:37,819 --> 01:11:38,380
[SPEAKER_01] uglavnom,

1316
01:11:38,380 --> 01:11:40,340
[SPEAKER_01] evo i ovim neurološkim,

1317
01:11:40,340 --> 01:11:41,159
[SPEAKER_01] između ostalog,

1318
01:11:41,159 --> 01:11:42,720
[SPEAKER_01] znači spomenula sam Parkinson,

1319
01:11:42,720 --> 01:11:44,399
[SPEAKER_01] ali je i depresija je recimo,

1320
01:11:44,399 --> 01:11:46,279
[SPEAKER_01] možda ni udar čak ima,

1321
01:11:46,279 --> 01:11:47,279
[SPEAKER_01] isto nekih,

1322
01:11:47,279 --> 01:11:49,500
[SPEAKER_01] ono kao da se nešto dogodi

1323
01:11:49,500 --> 01:11:50,819
[SPEAKER_01] prethodno u tim crjevima,

1324
01:11:50,819 --> 01:11:51,979
[SPEAKER_01] pa se ne izlučuje

1325
01:11:51,979 --> 01:11:54,979
[SPEAKER_01] ona količina protektivnih tvare

1326
01:11:54,979 --> 01:11:56,039
[SPEAKER_01] koje nam je potrebno

1327
01:11:56,039 --> 01:11:58,439
[SPEAKER_01] da bi funkcionirali dobro.

1328
01:11:58,439 --> 01:12:00,699
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da je užasno važno to područje.

1329
01:12:00,699 --> 01:12:01,420
[SPEAKER_01] I sad je ja,

1330
01:12:01,420 --> 01:12:03,560
[SPEAKER_01] na sreću se jako istražuje puno,

1331
01:12:03,560 --> 01:12:05,380
[SPEAKER_01] sad imate sve silne ove

1332
01:12:05,380 --> 01:12:06,520
[SPEAKER_01] probiotike,

1333
01:12:06,520 --> 01:12:07,500
[SPEAKER_01] prebiotike,

1334
01:12:07,500 --> 01:12:10,380
[SPEAKER_01] govori se šta od hrane treba jesti,

1335
01:12:10,380 --> 01:12:11,659
[SPEAKER_01] šta treba izbjegavati,

1336
01:12:11,659 --> 01:12:14,140
[SPEAKER_01] šta ste imate ono food for brain,

1337
01:12:14,140 --> 01:12:15,039
[SPEAKER_01] food not for,

1338
01:12:15,039 --> 01:12:16,239
[SPEAKER_01] mislim sve moguće,

1339
01:12:16,239 --> 01:12:17,979
[SPEAKER_01] razne upute

1340
01:12:17,979 --> 01:12:19,720
[SPEAKER_01] i baš je jako puno

1341
01:12:19,720 --> 01:12:21,439
[SPEAKER_01] i u literaturi ovo je prisutno

1342
01:12:21,439 --> 01:12:23,720
[SPEAKER_01] i ono, mislim i za lajke isto,

1343
01:12:23,720 --> 01:12:25,119
[SPEAKER_01] jako puno znanja sad

1344
01:12:25,119 --> 01:12:26,619
[SPEAKER_01] na sreću se plasira

1345
01:12:26,619 --> 01:12:27,880
[SPEAKER_01] i puno se o tom govori,

1346
01:12:27,880 --> 01:12:30,079
[SPEAKER_01] ima i ti podcasta isto puno

1347
01:12:30,079 --> 01:12:32,819
[SPEAKER_01] o zdravlju crjeva i mozga,

1348
01:12:32,819 --> 01:12:34,960
[SPEAKER_01] jer je to očito povezano jako.

1349
01:12:36,520 --> 01:12:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Došli smo do onog dijela

1350
01:12:38,000 --> 01:12:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] i zapravo onoga što mi možemo napraviti.

1351
01:12:41,000 --> 01:12:46,380
[SPEAKER_00] Jako je čest narativ genetike

1352
01:12:46,380 --> 01:12:48,760
[SPEAKER_00] i onoga što smo dobili rođenjem,

1353
01:12:48,760 --> 01:12:50,079
[SPEAKER_00] što smo dobili od svojih predaka.

1354
01:12:50,079 --> 01:12:54,560
[SPEAKER_00] Kako komentirate recimo epigenetiku

1355
01:12:54,560 --> 01:12:58,060
[SPEAKER_00] i kako komentirate zapravo

1356
01:12:58,060 --> 01:13:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] našu sposobnost da kroz dizajniranje životnog stila

1357
01:13:02,000 --> 01:13:06,279
[SPEAKER_00] utječemo na promjenu svog,

1358
01:13:06,520 --> 01:13:09,960
[SPEAKER_00] općenitog stanja bića,

1359
01:13:09,960 --> 01:13:11,199
[SPEAKER_00] zdravstvenog stanja i tako dalje

1360
01:13:11,199 --> 01:13:14,460
[SPEAKER_00] kroz svoje navike i svakodnevne neke aktivnosti?

1361
01:13:14,460 --> 01:13:16,880
[SPEAKER_01] Super pitanje, odnosno konstatacija.

1362
01:13:16,880 --> 01:13:18,439
[SPEAKER_00] Da, konstatacija.

1363
01:13:18,439 --> 01:13:22,680
[SPEAKER_01] 70-ih godina kad smo mi pronašli DNA, RNA i tako dalje

1364
01:13:22,680 --> 01:13:24,439
[SPEAKER_01] i kad smo rekao, evo, kromozomi,

1365
01:13:24,439 --> 01:13:28,640
[SPEAKER_01] genetika, mi nemiramo niš protiv svoje genetske karte,

1366
01:13:28,640 --> 01:13:31,399
[SPEAKER_01] s tim smo rođeni i tako će nam se onda dogoditi

1367
01:13:31,399 --> 01:13:33,079
[SPEAKER_01] ove bolesti i tako dalje.

1368
01:13:33,779 --> 01:13:36,380
[SPEAKER_01] I onda je na 100 godina, bila je onda tada,

1369
01:13:36,380 --> 01:13:40,979
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, jako puno je se o tom pisalo,

1370
01:13:40,979 --> 01:13:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] radilo, dakle, genetika je otkrivena

1371
01:13:43,000 --> 01:13:44,979
[SPEAKER_01] i ne možemo se mi protiv nje boriti.

1372
01:13:44,979 --> 01:13:47,520
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, onda na sreću su postojali ljudi

1373
01:13:47,520 --> 01:13:48,779
[SPEAKER_01] kao što je Bruce Lipton,

1374
01:13:48,779 --> 01:13:51,100
[SPEAKER_01] koji je malo se umorio od toga,

1375
01:13:51,100 --> 01:13:53,119
[SPEAKER_01] on je i studentima pričao o toj genetici,

1376
01:13:53,119 --> 01:13:56,699
[SPEAKER_01] onda je shvatio da je to zapravo malo ipak pretirano,

1377
01:13:57,199 --> 01:13:59,720
[SPEAKER_01] toliko se, to je onda znači de facto,

1378
01:13:59,720 --> 01:14:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] ti puštaš sudbilu svoju ruke genetici i ne želiš si pomoći na neki način,

1379
01:14:06,000 --> 01:14:08,079
[SPEAKER_01] znači to je defetistički stav totalno,

1380
01:14:08,079 --> 01:14:09,619
[SPEAKER_01] da ne možeš ništa pravit protiv.

1381
01:14:09,619 --> 01:14:12,199
[SPEAKER_01] I onda je eksperiment napravio,

1382
01:14:12,199 --> 01:14:13,859
[SPEAKER_01] pa je podokazao da se zapravo,

1383
01:14:14,840 --> 01:14:17,439
[SPEAKER_01] možemo mi svoj mislima masu toga napraviti,

1384
01:14:17,439 --> 01:14:19,079
[SPEAKER_01] možemo kompletno promijeniti,

1385
01:14:19,079 --> 01:14:22,039
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, aktivirajući neuroplastičnost,

1386
01:14:22,039 --> 01:14:24,300
[SPEAKER_01] promijeniti, znači, i izlječiti se,

1387
01:14:24,300 --> 01:14:26,960
[SPEAKER_01] i napraviti masu stvari za boljitak svoj,

1388
01:14:26,960 --> 01:14:28,939
[SPEAKER_01] i dulje živjeti, zdravije živjeti,

1389
01:14:28,939 --> 01:14:29,640
[SPEAKER_01] i sve ostalo.

1390
01:14:29,640 --> 01:14:31,680
[SPEAKER_01] Onda su ga tamo, oni njegovi kolege,

1391
01:14:31,680 --> 01:14:33,460
[SPEAKER_01] malo krivo gledali,

1392
01:14:33,460 --> 01:14:36,319
[SPEAKER_01] pa je zapravo nije više poslije bio na St. Farbeg,

1393
01:14:36,319 --> 01:14:37,680
[SPEAKER_01] je otišao negde na Karibe,

1394
01:14:37,680 --> 01:14:39,640
[SPEAKER_01] i tamo živi i uživa i predaje,

1395
01:14:39,640 --> 01:14:43,060
[SPEAKER_01] i dokazuje sve ovo što je on rekao,

1396
01:14:43,100 --> 01:14:46,380
[SPEAKER_01] de facto je, epigenetika je nešto,

1397
01:14:46,380 --> 01:14:47,720
[SPEAKER_01] znači, utjecaj okoline,

1398
01:14:47,720 --> 01:14:49,159
[SPEAKER_01] utjecaj naših misli,

1399
01:14:49,159 --> 01:14:52,020
[SPEAKER_01] utjecaj različitih impulsa iz okoline,

1400
01:14:52,020 --> 01:14:53,680
[SPEAKER_01] je taj koji je važan,

1401
01:14:53,680 --> 01:14:56,439
[SPEAKER_01] i mi moramo to osvijestiti i micati.

1402
01:14:56,439 --> 01:14:59,199
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, sad baš smo najdugo imali neka israživanja,

1403
01:14:59,199 --> 01:15:01,539
[SPEAKER_01] da čak eapoljušen,

1404
01:15:01,539 --> 01:15:03,140
[SPEAKER_01] zagađenje zraka,

1405
01:15:03,140 --> 01:15:04,739
[SPEAKER_01] je jedan od čimbenika rizika,

1406
01:15:04,739 --> 01:15:07,100
[SPEAKER_01] koji može utjecati loše na to,

1407
01:15:07,100 --> 01:15:08,479
[SPEAKER_01] da dođe do moženog udara,

1408
01:15:08,479 --> 01:15:10,579
[SPEAKER_01] do srčenog udara, do povišenog tlaka.

1409
01:15:10,579 --> 01:15:12,640
[SPEAKER_01] Neči, jesmo, baš ono što sam rekla,

1410
01:15:12,699 --> 01:15:14,500
[SPEAKER_01] svi smo jedni s drugima povezani,

1411
01:15:14,500 --> 01:15:16,880
[SPEAKER_01] i atmosferski tlak je taj koji djeluje

1412
01:15:16,880 --> 01:15:18,300
[SPEAKER_01] na naš tlak u organizmu,

1413
01:15:18,300 --> 01:15:20,260
[SPEAKER_01] znači, to sve je

1414
01:15:20,260 --> 01:15:21,859
[SPEAKER_01] zaista u vezi,

1415
01:15:21,859 --> 01:15:24,020
[SPEAKER_01] i mi smo ti koji možemo,

1416
01:15:24,020 --> 01:15:26,420
[SPEAKER_01] moramo prepoznaći što od toga

1417
01:15:26,420 --> 01:15:28,600
[SPEAKER_01] kod nas nije usklađeno

1418
01:15:28,600 --> 01:15:29,439
[SPEAKER_01] na neki način,

1419
01:15:29,439 --> 01:15:32,840
[SPEAKER_01] i onda to u svom životnom stilu stvarno možemo promijeniti.

1420
01:15:32,840 --> 01:15:34,460
[SPEAKER_01] Jer je to mogućnost

1421
01:15:34,460 --> 01:15:35,739
[SPEAKER_01] da onda stvarno ljudi žive

1422
01:15:35,739 --> 01:15:37,520
[SPEAKER_01] zdravije i bolje,

1423
01:15:37,520 --> 01:15:39,600
[SPEAKER_01] ali to je sve na bazi te neuroplastičnosti,

1424
01:15:39,600 --> 01:15:42,039
[SPEAKER_01] su dokazano sve, znači, to su mehanizmi koje,

1425
01:15:42,300 --> 01:15:43,560
[SPEAKER_01] Bog je to smislio,

1426
01:15:43,560 --> 01:15:45,680
[SPEAKER_01] da bi nam mozak omogućio da ga

1427
01:15:45,680 --> 01:15:47,460
[SPEAKER_01] možemo, znači,

1428
01:15:47,460 --> 01:15:49,159
[SPEAKER_01] kako bih nekada, držati zdravi,

1429
01:15:49,159 --> 01:15:51,640
[SPEAKER_01] mijenjajući te svoje i misli,

1430
01:15:51,640 --> 01:15:54,100
[SPEAKER_01] i imunitet,

1431
01:15:54,100 --> 01:15:55,819
[SPEAKER_01] i sve ovo ostalo,

1432
01:15:55,819 --> 01:15:57,739
[SPEAKER_01] znači, i boreći se protiv

1433
01:15:57,739 --> 01:15:58,920
[SPEAKER_01] kroničnog stresa, ne,

1434
01:15:58,920 --> 01:15:59,319
[SPEAKER_01] jer mislim,

1435
01:15:59,319 --> 01:16:01,119
[SPEAKER_01] to možemo puno napraviti,

1436
01:16:01,119 --> 01:16:01,640
[SPEAKER_01] mi u tom,

1437
01:16:02,020 --> 01:16:03,399
[SPEAKER_01] to je kronični stres i nešto što,

1438
01:16:03,399 --> 01:16:05,399
[SPEAKER_01] znači, to je ono što sam na početu spomenula,

1439
01:16:05,399 --> 01:16:07,220
[SPEAKER_01] ili mijenjaš,

1440
01:16:07,220 --> 01:16:08,619
[SPEAKER_01] ili te prilagođavaš,

1441
01:16:08,619 --> 01:16:11,319
[SPEAKER_01] a kronični stres je zapravo kad se ne prilagodiš

1442
01:16:11,319 --> 01:16:12,159
[SPEAKER_01] i ne mijenjaš,

1443
01:16:12,159 --> 01:16:15,199
[SPEAKER_01] nego se daš mlijet od nečega ti ne paše,

1444
01:16:15,279 --> 01:16:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

1445
01:16:16,000 --> 01:16:17,979
[SPEAKER_01] ako je neki mobig na poslu,

1446
01:16:17,979 --> 01:16:19,239
[SPEAKER_01] on se mićeš iz tog posla,

1447
01:16:19,239 --> 01:16:20,579
[SPEAKER_01] ako te nervira,

1448
01:16:20,579 --> 01:16:21,960
[SPEAKER_01] neću reći sad,

1449
01:16:21,960 --> 01:16:22,819
[SPEAKER_01] muž ili žena,

1450
01:16:22,819 --> 01:16:24,220
[SPEAKER_01] onda se mićeš iz tog,

1451
01:16:24,220 --> 01:16:25,600
[SPEAKER_01] iz te situacije,

1452
01:16:25,600 --> 01:16:25,920
[SPEAKER_01] jel tak,

1453
01:16:25,920 --> 01:16:27,020
[SPEAKER_01] ako te ne vjeraju desa,

1454
01:16:27,020 --> 01:16:28,880
[SPEAKER_01] onda njih pašaljaš da idu nekom drugom,

1455
01:16:28,880 --> 01:16:30,880
[SPEAKER_01] mami ili baki,

1456
01:16:30,880 --> 01:16:31,340
[SPEAKER_01] jel tak,

1457
01:16:31,340 --> 01:16:31,760
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

1458
01:16:31,760 --> 01:16:32,359
[SPEAKER_01] mislim,

1459
01:16:32,359 --> 01:16:34,100
[SPEAKER_01] neke stvari se stvarno mogu,

1460
01:16:34,100 --> 01:16:35,340
[SPEAKER_01] ne smijemo to,

1461
01:16:35,340 --> 01:16:37,380
[SPEAKER_01] niš simplificirano ne smijemo gledati,

1462
01:16:37,380 --> 01:16:38,300
[SPEAKER_01] to je kompleksno sve,

1463
01:16:38,300 --> 01:16:38,579
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

1464
01:16:38,579 --> 01:16:40,819
[SPEAKER_01] imati na umu da smo mi ipak

1465
01:16:40,819 --> 01:16:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] na neki način gospodari svoje sudbine,

1466
01:16:44,000 --> 01:16:44,380
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

1467
01:16:44,380 --> 01:16:45,420
[SPEAKER_01] nisu ti geni,

1468
01:16:45,420 --> 01:16:46,800
[SPEAKER_01] oni jesu odrednica,

1469
01:16:46,800 --> 01:16:47,819
[SPEAKER_01] ne mogu reći da nisu,

1470
01:16:47,819 --> 01:16:48,180
[SPEAKER_01] mislim,

1471
01:16:48,180 --> 01:16:49,060
[SPEAKER_01] sve što je pa mi,

1472
01:16:49,060 --> 01:16:52,699
[SPEAKER_01] znači da je boja očiju i ne znam kaj je zapravo vezana na tu genetskup,

1473
01:16:52,699 --> 01:16:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

1474
01:16:53,000 --> 01:16:53,600
[SPEAKER_01] ali,

1475
01:16:53,600 --> 01:16:54,239
[SPEAKER_01] na primjer,

1476
01:16:54,239 --> 01:16:56,819
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam znala reći pacijentima kada ono kažu,

1477
01:16:56,819 --> 01:16:57,260
[SPEAKER_01] ma,

1478
01:16:57,260 --> 01:16:58,960
[SPEAKER_01] moja mama je umrla od moženog udara,

1479
01:16:58,960 --> 01:17:00,399
[SPEAKER_01] tata je imao Alzheimer,

1480
01:17:00,399 --> 01:17:01,199
[SPEAKER_01] onda šta sad,

1481
01:17:01,199 --> 01:17:02,119
[SPEAKER_01] ja mogu i pušiti,

1482
01:17:02,119 --> 01:17:02,779
[SPEAKER_01] piti onak,

1483
01:17:02,779 --> 01:17:04,159
[SPEAKER_01] neću niš promijeniti,

1484
01:17:04,260 --> 01:17:05,520
[SPEAKER_01] neće se to isto dogoditi,

1485
01:17:05,520 --> 01:17:06,039
[SPEAKER_01] e sad,

1486
01:17:06,039 --> 01:17:06,659
[SPEAKER_01] to neće,

1487
01:17:06,659 --> 01:17:06,979
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

1488
01:17:06,979 --> 01:17:10,460
[SPEAKER_01] ti možeš kompletno baš sa takvom obiteljskom analizom,

1489
01:17:10,460 --> 01:17:13,260
[SPEAKER_01] možeš djelovati na sebe da se ne razboliš,

1490
01:17:13,260 --> 01:17:13,479
[SPEAKER_01] jel,

1491
01:17:13,479 --> 01:17:13,819
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

1492
01:17:13,819 --> 01:17:14,680
[SPEAKER_01] ali to,

1493
01:17:14,680 --> 01:17:15,100
[SPEAKER_01] zato,

1494
01:17:15,100 --> 01:17:17,500
[SPEAKER_01] mislim da je bitno da se o tom govori,

1495
01:17:17,500 --> 01:17:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] da se ljudima ukazuje da je,

1496
01:17:19,000 --> 01:17:21,739
[SPEAKER_01] ta epigenetika je snažna i zaista se,

1497
01:17:21,739 --> 01:17:22,159
[SPEAKER_01] pa,

1498
01:17:22,159 --> 01:17:24,159
[SPEAKER_01] evo ono što smo pričali o onim ljudima,

1499
01:17:24,159 --> 01:17:25,260
[SPEAKER_01] kak su malo,

1500
01:17:25,260 --> 01:17:27,699
[SPEAKER_01] bili ono kao pomlađeni,

1501
01:17:27,699 --> 01:17:28,359
[SPEAKER_01] to je isto ta,

1502
01:17:28,359 --> 01:17:29,899
[SPEAKER_01] oni su promijenili okolić,

1503
01:17:29,899 --> 01:17:30,680
[SPEAKER_01] bili su nekako iz,

1504
01:17:31,020 --> 01:17:31,960
[SPEAKER_01] tam je, ne znam,

1505
01:17:31,960 --> 01:17:33,720
[SPEAKER_01] namješta iz 70-ih,

1506
01:17:33,720 --> 01:17:34,619
[SPEAKER_01] svirala je glazba,

1507
01:17:34,619 --> 01:17:35,739
[SPEAKER_01] čitali su te novine,

1508
01:17:35,739 --> 01:17:35,939
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

1509
01:17:35,939 --> 01:17:41,520
[SPEAKER_01] ta okolina je onda bila promijenjena u onom skladu tog što se željelo postići.

1510
01:17:41,520 --> 01:17:43,020
[SPEAKER_00] Kako to izgleda, recimo,

1511
01:17:43,020 --> 01:17:44,720
[SPEAKER_00] kroz vaš život,

1512
01:17:44,720 --> 01:17:46,640
[SPEAKER_00] iz osobne priče u praksi,

1513
01:17:46,640 --> 01:17:49,020
[SPEAKER_00] što se tiče životnog stila i tih navika,

1514
01:17:49,020 --> 01:17:51,380
[SPEAKER_00] koje su navike, recimo,

1515
01:17:51,380 --> 01:17:51,920
[SPEAKER_00] onako,

1516
01:17:51,920 --> 01:17:53,819
[SPEAKER_00] kako bi ih složili po prioritetima,

1517
01:17:53,819 --> 01:17:58,399
[SPEAKER_00] da su bitne koje najdominantnije utječu na kvalitetu našeg života,

1518
01:17:58,399 --> 01:17:58,979
[SPEAKER_00] našeg zdravlja,

1519
01:17:58,979 --> 01:18:00,279
[SPEAKER_00] koji su to?

1520
01:18:00,279 --> 01:18:01,880
[SPEAKER_00] Misli su vam prvena sve,

1521
01:18:01,880 --> 01:18:02,819
[SPEAKER_00] to je broj jedan.

1522
01:18:02,819 --> 01:18:04,060
[SPEAKER_00] Šta bi bilo dalje nekada,

1523
01:18:04,060 --> 01:18:04,779
[SPEAKER_00] tijelo vježba,

1524
01:18:04,779 --> 01:18:05,319
[SPEAKER_00] prehrana?

1525
01:18:05,319 --> 01:18:06,060
[SPEAKER_01] Obavezna, ne,

1526
01:18:06,060 --> 01:18:07,039
[SPEAKER_01] pa to sigurno je,

1527
01:18:07,039 --> 01:18:07,380
[SPEAKER_01] gledajte,

1528
01:18:07,380 --> 01:18:08,500
[SPEAKER_01] ovo su ti stupovi,

1529
01:18:08,500 --> 01:18:09,039
[SPEAKER_01] de facto,

1530
01:18:09,039 --> 01:18:10,520
[SPEAKER_01] zdravlja mozga,

1531
01:18:10,520 --> 01:18:12,199
[SPEAKER_01] tijelo vježba je jako važna,

1532
01:18:12,199 --> 01:18:12,899
[SPEAKER_01] zašto?

1533
01:18:12,899 --> 01:18:15,039
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ona vam za vrijeme tijelo vježbe,

1534
01:18:15,039 --> 01:18:19,600
[SPEAKER_01] vam se de facto povećava količina BDNF-a,

1535
01:18:19,600 --> 01:18:22,220
[SPEAKER_01] to je brain derived neurotrophic factor,

1536
01:18:22,220 --> 01:18:22,520
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam,

1537
01:18:22,520 --> 01:18:24,020
[SPEAKER_01] to neopće nema hrvatskog imena,

1538
01:18:24,020 --> 01:18:24,960
[SPEAKER_01] znači brain derived,

1539
01:18:24,960 --> 01:18:27,939
[SPEAKER_01] mi ga sami izlučujemo u hipokampusu,

1540
01:18:27,939 --> 01:18:28,920
[SPEAKER_01] to je dio mozga,

1541
01:18:28,920 --> 01:18:31,539
[SPEAKER_01] a taj neurotrophin je potreban

1542
01:18:31,539 --> 01:18:32,760
[SPEAKER_01] za pamćanje,

1543
01:18:32,760 --> 01:18:35,159
[SPEAKER_01] koncentraciju i za raspoloženje,

1544
01:18:35,159 --> 01:18:37,500
[SPEAKER_01] znači nama je za sve kognitivne funkcije

1545
01:18:37,500 --> 01:18:38,479
[SPEAKER_01] i za raspoloženje,

1546
01:18:38,479 --> 01:18:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] trebao taj BDNF.

1547
01:18:40,260 --> 01:18:41,720
[SPEAKER_01] Ljudi koji nemaju dovoljno,

1548
01:18:41,720 --> 01:18:43,239
[SPEAKER_01] jer ili su starili,

1549
01:18:43,239 --> 01:18:44,420
[SPEAKER_01] ili su se razbolili,

1550
01:18:44,420 --> 01:18:46,920
[SPEAKER_01] i te njihov hipokampus više ne izlučuje,

1551
01:18:46,920 --> 01:18:48,880
[SPEAKER_01] mitohondrije su im oslabili,

1552
01:18:48,880 --> 01:18:53,819
[SPEAKER_01] i dakle njemu treba nešto dodatno da ga aktivira,

1553
01:18:53,819 --> 01:18:55,260
[SPEAKER_01] a tu je tijelo vježba,

1554
01:18:55,260 --> 01:18:55,640
[SPEAKER_01] jer ona,

1555
01:18:55,640 --> 01:18:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali kod te tijelo vježbe je uvijek naglašana,

1556
01:18:59,000 --> 01:19:02,340
[SPEAKER_01] kak je najdivnija i najkompleksnija tijelo vježba,

1557
01:19:02,340 --> 01:19:03,460
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno fizička aktivnost,

1558
01:19:03,460 --> 01:19:04,380
[SPEAKER_01] vam je ples,

1559
01:19:04,380 --> 01:19:06,340
[SPEAKER_01] jer ples je ono fantazija,

1560
01:19:06,340 --> 01:19:07,859
[SPEAKER_01] zato što tu slušaš glazbu,

1561
01:19:07,960 --> 01:19:08,819
